goal: forall(x0: ℝ, x1: ℝ, x2: ℝ) { x0 ⋅ (x1 ⋅ x2) = x0 ⋅ x1 ⋅ x2 }
proof: let (s0: ℝ, s1: ℝ, s2: ℝ) satisfy { s0 ⋅ (s1 ⋅ s2) != s0 ⋅ s1 ⋅ s2 }

goal: forall(x0: ℝ, x1: ℝ, x2: ℝ) { (x0 + x1) ⋅ x2 = lib(type_class.add).P_Add.add[ℝ](x0 ⋅ x2, x1 ⋅ x2) }
proof: let (s0: ℝ, s1: ℝ, s2: ℝ) satisfy { s0 ⋅ s2 + s1 ⋅ s2 != (s0 + s1) ⋅ s2 }
let s0: ℝ satisfy { ℝ.1 ⋅ s0 != s0 }

goal: forall(x0: ℝ, x1: ℝ, x2: ℝ) { x0 ⋅ lib(type_class.add).P_Add.add[ℝ](x1, x2) = lib(type_class.add).P_Add.add[ℝ](x0 ⋅ x1, x0 ⋅ x2) }
proof: let (s0: ℝ, s1: ℝ, s2: ℝ) satisfy { s0 ⋅ s1 + s0 ⋅ s2 != s0 ⋅ (s1 + s2) }
let s0: ℝ satisfy { ℝ.0 ⋅ s0 != ℝ.0 }

goal: scal(-ℝ.1, v) + v = scal(-ℝ.1, v) + scal(ℝ.1, v)
scal(-ℝ.1, v) + scal(ℝ.1, v) = scal(-ℝ.1 + ℝ.1, v)
proof: V.scal(-ℝ.1, v) + V.scal(ℝ.1, v) = V.scal(-ℝ.1 + ℝ.1, v)
scal(-ℝ.1 + ℝ.1, v) = V.scal(-ℝ.1 + ℝ.1, v)
scal(-ℝ.1, v) + v != V.0 or scal(-ℝ.1, v) = -v

goal: exists(k0: ℕ, k1: ℕ -> V) { forall(x0: ℕ) { x0 >= k0 implies k1(x0) = V.0 } }
proof: let s1: (ℕ, ℕ -> V) -> ℕ satisfy { forall(x0: ℕ, x1: ℕ -> V) { s1(x0, x1) >= x0 } and forall(x2: ℕ -> V, x3: ℕ) { x2(s1(x3, x2)) != V.0 } }
